name: Keisha Pedro
description:
Im KEISHA PEDRO, I am fit, ambitious, I can also be characterized as immensely likable; a woman of energy, talents; and one who has inclination for fun.
What I am looking for is a confident, attractive and vibrant man who also happens to be intelligent and kind-hearted.
I am an active entrepreneur looking for an intelligent partner who has achieved his own satisfying independent life, but who also wants to be in a loving relationship. I’m drawn to bright
Friends would describe me as thoughtful, highly intelligent, sophisticated, sincere, reliable, trustworthy, physically active, optimistic, loving and caring. Im fairly traditional, with strong character and core values.
I am a type of woman who will make time for my relationship and the important man in my life. I am also a fun-loving lady with a wary sense of humor and I appreciate wit in my partner.
